snippet.title: 100% Orange Juice - Mei & Natsumi Character Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Mei (VA: Satou Megumi 佐藤 恵) and Natsumi (VA: Maruyama Miki 丸山 美紀) are now available to play in 100% Orange Juice - Mei & Natsumi Character Pack on Steam!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/955130/100_Orange_Juice__Mei__Natsumi_Character_Pack/

100% Orange Juice is a digital multiplayer board game populated by developer Orange Juice's all-star cast. Characters from Flying Red Barrel, QP Shooting, Suguri and Sora come together with all-new characters to duke it out... with dice.
